Add to cron:
0	0	*	*	*	/bin/bash -l -c "cd /home/prometheusapp/www/prometheus2.0 && rake RAILS_ENV=production sisyphus:groups sisyphusarm:groups platform5:groups 51:groups 50:groups 41:groups 40:groups 50:acls 50:leaders 50:teams 41:acls 41:leaders 41:teams 40:acls 40:leaders 40:teams >> /var/log/prometheus.log 2>&1"
